parameters: \n<Demon>Climbing up my leg like a bug... Get off of
there! I'll teach you a lesson when I get enough
mana back to move.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Sorry, I'll be using your mana for these
seals I have.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Now it's time to find those mana points.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>... I can see it from here. Looks like
it's pretty close to her stomach.
\n<Demon>M-My stomach? Hey, don't you dare touch there! I
haven't been moving around that much lately so it's-
AlainFace
\n<Alain>What? Are you worried about a bit of fat?
I didn't know succubi could act so self-
conscious. It's pretty cute.
\n<Demon>C-Cute? Are you stupid, you speck of a man?
A
AlainFace
\n<Alain>This is the Black Ruby? It doesn't seem
that dangerous... or black, but that might
just be because it's still under the
demon's control.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>A lot of monster materials become more
uncontrolled when the monster is slain or
when we salvage them.
\n<Demon>Slain?! So you're after me for materials? So you
ARE with those bastards who were chasing me!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Bastards chasing you? Unless the Guild's
got you on a list, we're an independent
pair of adventurers.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>This should only extract neutralize
the cursed energy too - not kill her.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>I'm curious, but, for now, let's trace
where her mana is flowing from here...
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Looks like it's down her arm somewhere.
A
\n<Demon>Hey, quit it! I can feel your crawling and it's
itching like crazy.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Well this might sting more than it'd
itch. Take this!
\n<Demon>Sucking up my mana like a mosquito? You really
are like a bug!
\n<Demon>Just when I thought having to hide out in these
ruins was tough enough...
\v[18]/5 seals placed on Demon.
A
HP and SP were fully recovered!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Ooh. This is a nice design. Is it a
butterfly?
\n<Demon>Heh. You like what you see? If you stop what
you're doing, I can show you else I have underneath
my clothes.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Was that supposed to seduce me? It doesn't
look like you have any charm magic without
your mana.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Well, don't take that as an insult. You're
plenty beautiful without it.
\n<Demon>Beauti-? W-W-What are you saying at a time
like this?
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Okay... Let's trace where her mana is
flowing from here...
AlainFace
\n<Alain>It's nearby... Up top?
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Of course it'd be right between titanic
breasts of hers!
\n<Demon>Hey, don't ignore me!
A
AlainFace
\n<Alain>These massive milkers would be alluring
on any normal day, but from a demon that's
strong enough to give Gale a hard time,
it's equally as intimidating.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Is there a word for arousing and
frightening at the same time? Succubi
definitely bring about that feeling with
their power and sex appeal.
\n<Demon>Grr... Just seeing you climb between my boobs and
being unable to do anything about it is irritating...
\n<Demon>Once I get my mana back, I'm going to have my
way with you. Don't count on coming back alive.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Sorry, but I won't be staying alive.
You won't be getting any mana on my watch.
\v[18]/5 seals placed on Demon.
A
AlainFace
\n<Alain>And that's the last one! Alright. It's
time to activate the sealing barrier.
\n<Demon>A sealing barrier...? You're doing all this just
for my Blood Ruby?!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Sorry. This is all part of the job as
an adventurer. Gale! It's time!
Blackout
SpriteZoom.zoom(0, 1);
AlainFace
\n<Alain>*cough* Blah. It's not just mana pooling
over here. Her sweat's been festering
under her armpit too. It stinks.
\n<Demon>Sti-!? Don't complain! It's not my fault I've
been stuck here for a long time. Succubi are supposed

\v[18]/5 seals placed on Demon.
A
\n<Demon>Hey, just what do you think you're doing there?
AlainFace
\n<Alain>You don't have to worry. This won't
be for too long.
\v[18]/5 seals placed on Demon.
A
\n<Demon>H-Hey! Not the tail! I'm really sensitive there!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>If you tell me something like that, it
just makes me want to do it more!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Okay - let's trace her mana from
here...
\n<Demon>Nggnh! Hyaaah~n!
\n<Demon>... Damn tiny human... I just need to scoot

AlainFace
\n<Alain>Sorry, but since you can't move, it's'
too late. I've got my target.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Up her right arm? Okay. That should be
easy to do.
A
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Heh. It's not as a bad as I thought. Did
you really think it was all flabby? You're
actually really fit.
\n<Demon>Hey, I told you not to get on there!
\n<Demon>And I know I've gotten a little fat cooped up
in these ruins. Don't try to reassure me with lies!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>So overly-conscious... I'm so glad Gale
doesn't act like this.
\v[18]/5 seals placed on Demon.
A
\n<Demon>Why you... Skittering around on my skin like a bug.
Could you at least move more gently? You're steps
are tickling me...
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Heh. Saying that only makes me want
to take harder steps.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Okay... Let's trace where her mana is
flowing from here...
AlainFace
\n<Alain>It's going up her left leg...? Okay.
I'll have to climb up then.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>As expected of a succubus-type demon -
every part of her body has curves.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>If she were able to move right now, I'd
be completely squished flat by a simple
shift of her leg.
A
AlainFace
\n<Alain>*cough* Gah! After all that fighting,
this demon's body has gotten hot, but this
place is another beast entirely.
\n<Demon>What the-!? What are you doing crawling over there?
Having your way with me just because I can't move?
AlainFace
\n<Alain>What? No, I- I mean, I was just-
I mean, it's not like that!
\n<Demon>You humans are all the same when you see a pretty
face. And now that I'm helpless, even a shrunken insect
like you thinks he can have a shot.
\n<Demon>Well, you picked the wrong demon to mess with. A
succubus is strongest right there!
AlainFace
\n<Alain>What? Even though she's exhausted her
mana from our fight?
\n<Demon>Fufufu... Thanks for the mana... That should be
enough for me to at least do this!
Blackout
DemonC4
AlainFace
\n<Alain>W-What?! Her tail?! It wasn't moving
earlier! No way, did she really take some
of my mana?
\n<Demon>I caught you, little guy. Now, hold still. I'm
going to suck all I can out of you while I can.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Hngh?! She's not just absorbing my mana
is she? Wait- Any lower and you'll-
DemonC3
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Mgfff!?
\n<Demon>That'll shut you up. You adventurers may have
labeled us succubi as kinky demons but I'm not a fan
of having any eyes watching me do the deed.
\n<Demon>Now sit still and take it like a man. Your
vitality, your mana, your emotions - I'll eat them
all through my pussy.
AlainFace
\n<Alain>Mgfff...! (I can't breathe... She's
stroking with her tail with such ferocity
and such... sensuality...)
Blackout
\n<Demon>Aaaah~~~n! This isn't much different from
playing with myself, but it must be a whole world of
difference to you, little guy.
\n<Demon>You'll be my fuel to get back on my feet. And then
your friend will be the same.
\n<Demon>Let that be a lesson to you for trying to take
on a demon - even a cornered succubus like me.
Having chosen the worst possible location to be near
a succubus Dragon Rider Alain re-energized the demon
succubus he had thought they had defeated.
Her finger and tail were all she needed. He was so
small that he was easily caught when the succubus
demon was able to move even the slightest bit.
Forced to take be the titanic demon's masturbation aid,
the shrunken adventurer had his mana and vitality
entirely drained before Gale could wake up.
